"{\"uid\": \"breakingnews.ie-world-man-who-stabbed-french-soldier-ahead-of-olympics-taken-to-psychiatric-hospital-1650496.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home  The Buzz  Sport  Quiz  Explained  Trending  Mobile menu  Theme  Home  The Buzz  Sport  Quiz  Explained  Trending  Search modal  By Associated Press Reporters  The man who stabbed and wounded a French soldier patrolling Paris just days before the opening ceremony of the 2024 Olympics has been taken to a psychiatric hospital, French prosecutors said on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 137, \"end\": 153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999961316234265, \"rank\": 3.868391463180602e-06, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 199, \"end\": 205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9894386211575784, \"rank\": 0.009989549345266304, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 225, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.35932106471283e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 332, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9894386211575784, \"rank\": 0.009989549345266304, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The attack happened outside the Gare de l'Est station in eastern Paris on Monday.\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.35932106471283e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The city has been under a high security alert before the start of the Summer Games on July 26.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The soldier was taken to hospital suffering from a shoulder blade injury, but was not in life-threatening condition, officials said after the attack.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The stabbing happened outside the Gare de l'Est station in eastern Paris on Monday (Paul Thompson Live News/Alamy/PA)    A statement from the Paris Public Prosecutor's office on Tuesday identified the attacker as 40-year-old Christian Ingondo, who was born in Congo.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.35932106471283e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.35932106471283e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 847, \"end\": 864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"score\": 0.9999999878768905, \"rank\": 1.212315952653182e-08, \"text\": \"Public Prosecutor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\"}, {\"begin\": 924, \"end\": 933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc